metadata.name: Yant Tech
metadata.description:
Yant Tech : Choose your daily yant for protection before you go outside

Yant - is a form of tattooing using sacred geometrical, animal and deity designs along with Pali phrases that are said to offer power, protection, fortune, charisma and other benefits for the carrier.

3000 x 3000 px
Animation loop

Artwork by Guidekk   l   2021
